name: Jetvoy
description: Jetvoy is a next-generation token designed to power innovation at the intersection of travel, luxury, and digital finance. Inspired by the speed and freedom of jet travel, Jetvoy provides utility across decentralized applications, travel-based loyalty systems, and premium membership ecosystems. With a focus on fast transactions, global accessibility, and high-end digital experiences, Jetvoy represents the fusion of futuristic mobility and blockchain technology.
